{"id":17907,"date":"2022-12-31T04:17:31","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:17:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/vimexpo-noi-nhin-ro-thuc-trang-noi-dia-hoa-o-to-tai-viet-nam.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:17:31","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:17:31","slug":"vimexpo-noi-nhin-ro-thuc-trang-noi-dia-hoa-o-to-tai-viet-nam-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/vimexpo-noi-nhin-ro-thuc-trang-noi-dia-hoa-o-to-tai-viet-nam-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Vimexpo \u2013 n\u01a1i nh\u00ecn r\u00f5 th\u1ef1c tr\u1ea1ng n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba h\u00f3a \u00f4 t\u00f4 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn, ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 khai m\u1ea1c s\u00e1ng 16\/11, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Vimexpo 2022 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Trung t\u00e2m Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (ICE), v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a h\u01a1n 200 doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 300 gian h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean di\u1ec7n t\u00edch tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y 5.000 m2.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf tham gia tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m nh\u01b0 Thaco, Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam, T\u1ed5ng c\u00f4ng ty M\u00e1y \u0110\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 M\u00e1y N\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p (VEAM), Samsung, Toshiba Asia\u2026 C\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.  ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u00f4 t\u00f4, c\u01a1 kh\u00ed ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o, c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 cao, \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u00e1c l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c li\u00ean quan.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Kh\u00e1ch tham quan m\u1ed9t gian h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m n\u0103m nay.  \u1ea2nh: Vimexpo\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/vimexpo-noi-nhin-ro-thuc-trang-noi-dia-hoa.jpg\" title=\"vimexpo-noi-nhin-ro-thuc-trang-noi-dia-hoa\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/vimexpo-noi-nhin-ro-thuc-trang-noi-dia-hoa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/vimexpo-noi-nhin-ro-thuc-trang-noi-dia-hoa-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/vimexpo-noi-nhin-ro-thuc-trang-noi-dia-hoa.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Kh\u00e1ch tham quan m\u1ed9t gian h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m n\u0103m nay.  \u1ea2nh: Vimexpo<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Vimexpo l\u00e0 n\u01a1i c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng quan t\u00e2m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 b\u1ee9c tranh v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba h\u00f3a \u00f4 t\u00f4 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.  Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, Toyota mang \u0111\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m chi\u1ebfc Veloz l\u1eafp r\u00e1p, nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 tr\u1ee3.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">N\u1ebfu ng\u00e0nh n\u00e0y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng xe s\u1ebd b\u1edbt g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u linh ki\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3m m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n chi ph\u00ed s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn.  Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p CNHT Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn, ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m Vimexpo 2022 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra trong 3 ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 16-18\/11.  S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bthu h\u00fat kho\u1ea3ng 15.000 l\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00e1ch tham quan.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">M\u1ef9 \u2013 Anh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn, ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 khai m\u1ea1c s\u00e1ng 16\/11, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m doanh nghi\u1ec7p. Vimexpo 2022 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Trung t\u00e2m Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (ICE), v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a h\u01a1n 200 doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 300 gian [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":15978,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17907"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17907"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17907\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15978"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17907"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17907"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":tru